title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Celebrate the Day of the Dead with a Trio of Masks
content:
Day of the Dead provides an extra dose of otherworldly whimsy with a trio of masks including the Royal Calaca Mask, Romance Calaca Mask, and the Floral Calaca Mask.

Collect these ornate accessories by logging in to play GTA Online anytime this week.
